1\naiops-k8s-06,frontend,frontend-1,frontend-1,hipstershop.ShippingService/GetQuote,14,transport is closing,出现次数:1\naiops-k8s-08,frontend,frontend-2,frontend-2,hipstershop.ShippingService/GetQuote,14,transport is closing,出现次数:1\n", "matched_anomaly": "Determine the root cause of the system fault during 2025-06-20T23:10:09Z to 2025-06-20T23:35:09Z.", "time_range": "2025-06-20 23:10:09+00:00 to 2025-06-20 23:35:09+00:00"}, "trace_data_collected": true, "log_analysis_findings": "基于获取到的日志数据，我现在可以验证根因假设：\"shippingservice is the root cause due to port connection refused errors and complete service unavailability\"。\n\n**分析结果：**\n\n从日志数据中可以清晰地看到，所有错误都来自frontend服务，并且都指向同一个问题：无法连接到shippingservice的50051端口。\n\n**关键证据：**\n1. **明确的连接拒绝错误**：日志中反复出现 `\"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.27.213:50051: connect: connection refused\"`\n2. **目标服务明确**：IP地址10.233.27.213指向shippingservice\n3. **端口明确**：50051端口是shippingservice的标准服务端口\n4. **服务完全不可用**：错误类型包括`connection refused`和`transport is closing`，表明shippingservice完全无法响应\n\n**符合Port Misconfiguration模式：**\n- 特征：`connection refused` + 目标服务无法连接\n- 根据特殊故障模式识别规则，component应为被调方服务（shippingservice）\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"port\", \"connection refused\", \"transport\", \"Error while dialing\", \"transport is closing\", \"Unavailable\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"port connection refused errors causing complete service unavailability\",\n      \"evidence\": \"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.27.213:50051: connect: connection refused\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**结论**：根因假设成立。shippingservice确实是系统故障的根本原因，由于端口连接拒绝错误导致服务完全不可用。", "trace_analysis_findings": "Based on the trace data analysis, I can now validate the hypothesis that shippingservice is the root cause. The evidence strongly supports this conclusion.\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\"error_ratio\", \"frontend->shippingservice\", \"checkoutservice->shippingservice\", \"rrt_max\", \"checkoutservice->cartservice\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Connection refused errors (262+ occurrences) when frontend services attempt to connect to shippingservice at 10.233.27.213:50051. ShippingService/GetQuote shows complete unavailability with Fast Fail pattern (normal duration ~1900ms reduced to ~140ms)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\", \n      \"evidence\": \"CheckoutService/PlaceOrder shows significant latency increase from normal ~150s to anomaly ~58s, caused by shipping service failures cascading through the system\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice/redis\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Secondary performance degradation with HMSET operations increasing from ~1.3s to ~29.6s, likely due to system-wide resource contention\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**Key Evidence Supporting the Hypothesis:**\n\n1. **Direct Connection Refusal**: The trace data shows 262+ occurrences of \"connection refused\" errors when services try to connect to shippingservice at 10.233.27.213:50051.\n\n2. **Fast Fail Pattern**: ShippingService/GetQuote operations show a classic Fast Fail pattern - normal duration of ~1900ms drops to ~140ms during anomalies, indicating immediate connection refusal rather than timeout.\n\n3. **Error Propagation**: The errors cascade upward through the system:\n   - ShippingService unavailable (root cause)\n   - CheckoutService/PlaceOrder failures due to shipping quote unavailability\n   - Frontend HTTP 500 errors as the final symptom\n\n4. **Consistent Error Pattern**: The same IP address (10.233.27.213) and port (50051) appear across all connection refused errors, confirming a single point of failure.\n\nThe trace data provides clear evidence that shippingservice was completely unavailable due to connection refused errors, making it the primary root cause. Other performance issues (Redis, cartservice) appear to be secondary effects rather than primary causes.", "metric_analysis_findings": "基于获取到的Trace数据，我现在可以验证\"shippingservice是根因\"的假设。让我分析指标数据：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"error_ratio\", \"client_error_ratio\", \"rrt_max\", \"node_memory_usage_rate\", \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"shippingservice所有实例(error_ratio和client_error_ratio)出现严重错误率飙升，从0.0上升到57.6%，表明服务完全不可用\",\n      \"evidence\": \"shippingservice-0: error_ratio从0.0到57.6；shippingservice-1: error_ratio从0.0到47.5；shippingservice-2: error_ratio从0.0到57.0\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"frontend服务出现server_error_ratio和error_ratio异常，是shippingservice不可用的下游影响\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend-0: server_error_ratio从0.0到2.11；frontend-1: server_error_ratio从0.0到2.19；frontend-2: server_error_ratio从0.0到2.11\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"cartservice-1出现error_ratio和client_error_ratio异常，可能是连锁反应\",\n      \"evidence\": \"cartservice-1: error_ratio从0.0到37.5；client_error_ratio从0.0到37.5\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**分析结论**：我支持shippingservice是根因的假设，理由如下：\n\n1. **shippingservice完全不可用**：所有三个实例的`error_ratio`和`client_error_ratio`都从0.0飙升到47.5%-57.6%，表明服务完全不可用，这与\"port connection refused errors\"的描述一致。\n\n2. **下游服务受影响**：frontend服务的`server_error_ratio`和`error_ratio`异常，这是典型的shippingservice不可用导致的连锁反应。\n\n3. **其他服务异常是次要影响**：cartservice-1的错误率异常可能是系统整体不稳定导致的次要问题，而不是根因。\n\n4. **节点内存压力不是主要问题**：虽然aiops-k8s-03有内存可用性变化，但变化幅度相对较小，且shippingservice-2正好运行在该节点上，可能是shippingservice故障导致的内存压力。\n\n数据验证了shippingservice确实是故障的根因，其服务不可用导致了整个系统的级联故障。"}
